info.name: Disciline
info.description: Disciline is a RESTful API Student Offense Information System (SIPS) web application that aims to record, manage, and report offenses committed by students in the school environment. This application is designed to assist schools, such as teachers, homeroom teachers, and administrative staff, in monitoring and following up on student behavior effectively and efficiently.
